desc_long								关于这款游戏							Welcome soldier! You are a representative of a special military group dealing with specific tasks in the enemy's territory! If there is a lack of ammo, wounded soldiers, emergency situations, you have to be there! This special car is entrusted to you, in which you perform your job! As I mentioned, you will mainly operate in the enemy's territory, difficult tasks await you! I hope you are ready ... You must be! Prepare for difficult missions! Pedal to the metal!- You have to drive through difficult terrain and at the same time not destroy your  vehicle.- Be ready for a conflict against your enemy on his area.- You will have to choose a path that will decide the course of the mission!- In front of you difficult tasks, and you have to face it!- Diversified terrain, weather anomalies, it all affects the ride!						
